    "Background": {
      "text": "Explosive dermatosis with tender erythema, bullae, and subsequent exfolliation\nMost commonly caused by medications\nSulfa drugs,\npenicillins\n,\nanticonvulsants\n, and\nNSAIDs\nOther causes: infection, chemicals, malignancy, immunologic factors",
